<text top="55" left="90" width="103" height="13" font="1">Security Council</text>
<text top="55" left="733" width="95" height="13" font="1">3837th meeting</text>
<text top="73" left="90" width="141" height="14" font="1">Fifty-second Year year</text>
<text top="73" left="710" width="118" height="14" font="1">28 November 1997</text>
<text top="109" left="153" width="295" height="14" font="1">"The Security Council will remain seized of the</text>
<text top="127" left="122" width="327" height="14" font="1">matter and will consider whether additional action</text>
<text top="145" left="122" width="119" height="14" font="1">may be necessary."</text>
<text top="181" left="122" width="327" height="14" font="1">This statement will be issued as a document of the</text>
<text top="199" left="90" width="325" height="14" font="1">Security Council under the symbol S/PRST/1997/54.</text>
<text top="109" left="512" width="316" height="14" font="1">The Security Council has thus concluded the present</text>
<text top="127" left="481" width="321" height="14" font="1">stage of its consideration of the item on the agenda.</text>
<text top="163" left="512" width="316" height="14" font="1">The Security Council will remain seized of the</text>
<text top="181" left="481" width="42" height="14" font="1">matter.</text>
<text top="218" left="512" width="185" height="14" font="5"><i>The meeting rose at 1.50 p.m.</i></text>
<text top="1084" left="821" width="8" height="14" font="1">3</text>
</page>
